title: Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5
text:
> Indiana Lynx capture 3rd title in 5 years with 69-52 win in Game 5 Minnesota Lynx forward Maya Moore (23) celebrates after beating the Indiana Fever 69-52 in Game 5 of the WNBA basketball finals, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Minneapolis. (AP Photo/Jim Mone)
